Detailed Description

A definition usage citation.

Equality, Hashing, and Copying

WNDefinitionCitation instances implement NSObject's hash and isEqual methods, as well as the NSCopying protocol. Instances may be compared by value using NSObject::isEqual: and may be used as a key in NSDictionary.
